    "description": "Craftsvilla Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Digital Marketing Manager for our Gurgaon operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Craftsvilla Global Group:\nCraftsvilla Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Magento\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Craftsvilla Global Group!",
